SIMPLE: desegregate
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: desegregate
<hw>de*seg"re*gate</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to eliminate laws,
regulations, or customs which prohibit members of a specific racial or
national group from using (certain locations, organizations, or
facilities); to introduce members of a racial or religious group into (a
community, facility, or organization from which they had been
barred).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>desegregation</ent>⟦br⟧
